Package: EpiNova
Title: Flexible Extended State-Space Epidemiological Models with Modern Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Subir", "Hait",
           email = "haitsubi@msu.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-9871-9677"))
Description: 
    An extended epidemiological modeling framework that goes beyond the classical SIR 
    model. EpiNova supports SEIR, SEIRD, SVEIRD, and age-stratified compartmental 
    models with flexible intervention functions (spline-based, Gaussian process, or 
    user-defined). Inference is available via maximum likelihood or sequential Monte 
    Carlo (particle filtering). Includes real-time effective reproduction number (Rt) 
    estimation, spatial/network-aware multi-patch models, and ensemble forecasting 
    with proper uncertainty quantification.
